Bir Dilek Tut Benim İçin
Bir Dilek Tut Benim İçin () is İzel's sixth studio album. It was released in April 2005. This album has significant difference that she starts working with Sinan Akçıl. This album has songs mostly written by Sinan Akçıl. Also, there are three Sezen Aksu songs and a Özdemir Erdoğan song, called "Aç Kapıyı".
